! Emoji Picker Plugin

Insert emojis into your tiddlers using autocompletion.

!! Usage

Type `:` followed by an emoji name to trigger autocompletion:

* `:smile` - Shows emoji suggestions matching "smile"
* `:heart` - Shows heart-related emojis
* `:thumb` - Shows thumbs up/down emojis

Select an emoji from the dropdown to insert it.

!! Configuration

Enable/disable via ''Control Panel > Settings > CodeMirror > Autocompletion > Emoji picker''
